          <h4>We look forward to working with you!</h4>
          <p>—The Taiwanese Cultural Society at Stanford University</p>

        </div>

        <h2 data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#vendor-registration" class="clickable" style="cursor: pointer">Vendor Registration</h2>
        <div id="vendor-registration" class="collapse in">
          <h3>Please register before February 25th</h3>
          <p>E-mail vxiao at stanford.edu if you need to modify or cancel your registration.</p>

          <p>All information that you submit here can be changed up until <strong>February 25 at 9PM</strong> - please let us know before then if you need to modify or cancel your registration. Please note that the above agreement may change. Thank you!</p>
          <%= form_for :vendor, method: :post, url: {action: :post_registration}, html: {role: "form"} do |f| %>
            <fieldset>
              <legend>Vendor Package (Required)</legend>
            </fieldset>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <div class="radio col-sm-10">
                <%= f.radio_button :vendor_package, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-package-prepaid"%> Prepaid package ($260)
              </div>

              <div class="radio col-sm-10">
                <%= f.radio_button :vendor_package, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-package-bulk"%> Bulk package (no fee)
              </div>
            </div>

            <fieldset>
              <legend>Basic Information (Required)</legend>
            </fieldset>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-name" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Business Name</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_name, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-name", placeholder: "e.g. Taiwanese Cultural Society" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-address" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Business Address</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_address, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-address", placeholder: "e.g. 541 Lasuen Mall, Ste. 200, Stanford, CA 94305" %>
                <p class="form-text text-muted">Please provide the full address where your restaurant is registered (house number, street number, city, state, ZIP, et cetera.)</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <fieldset>
              <legend>Primary Contact (Required)</legend>
            </fieldset>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-primary-name" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Primary Contact Name</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_primary_name, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-primary-name", placeholder: "e.g. John Doe" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-primary-email" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Primary Contact E-mail</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_primary_email, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-primary-email", placeholder: "e.g. jdoe@stanford.edu" %>
                <p class="form-text text-muted">This is used as your login username.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-primary-phone" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Primary Contact Phone Number</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_primary_phone, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-primary-phone", placeholder: "e.g. 408.555.5555" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-preferred-contact" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Preferred Contact Method</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_preferred_contact, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-preferred-contact", placeholder: "e.g. email, phone" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-password" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Password</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.password_field :pass, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-password", placeholder: "Password (6 - 64 characters, please!)" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-password-confirmation" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Password Confirmation</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.password_field :pass_confirmation, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-password-confirmation", placeholder: "Password Confirmation" %>
              </div>
            </div>

            <fieldset>
              <legend>Secondary Contact (Optional)</legend>
            </fieldset>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-secondary-name" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Secondary Contact Person</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_secondary_name, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-secondary-name", placeholder: "e.g. Jane Doe" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-secondary-email" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Secondary Contact E-mail</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_secondary_email, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-secondary-email", placeholder: "e.g. jadoe@stanford.edu" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-secondary-phone" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Secondary Contact Phone Number</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_secondary_phone, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-secondary-phone", placeholder: "e.g. 408.555.5555" %>
              </div>
            </div>

            <fieldset>
              <legend>Booth Information</legend>
            </fieldset>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-food-information" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Food description (Required)</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_area :vendor_food_information, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-food-information", rows: 5, placeholder: "e.g. We can sell stir fry noodles for $4.50/serving (50 servings), fried rice for $4.00/serving (50 servings), and fried dumpling for $3.50/serving (40 servings)." %>
                <p class="form-text text-muted">Please let us know what you are able to prepare and sell along with approximate prices. All food must be pre-packaged individually (i.e. single serving size sealed box, cup, bag, or other container) and must come labelled with the time that it was packaged. Let us know if you have any questions about your food here.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-business-information" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Business description (Required)</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_area :vendor_description, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-business-information", rows: 5, placeholder: "e.g. The Stanford Night Market was founded in 1994 and aims to connect people to the beauty of Taiwanese culture..." %>
                <p class="form-text text-muted">Please enter a small blurb (one to two short paragraphs) about your restaurant (i.e. history, specialties, or anything you deem relevant!). This is for publicity purposes as we will feature vendors and their information on our website.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-website" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Business website (Optional)</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_website, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-website", placeholder: "e.g. taiwanese.stanford.edu" %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group row">
              <label for="vendor-photo" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Business photo (Optional)</label>
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <%= f.text_field :vendor_photo, class: "form-control", id: "vendor-photo", placeholder: "e.g. https://www.flickr.com/photos/128195661@N08/16920803364/" %>
                <p class="form-text text-muted">Please submit a link to a photo of your business for publicity purposes. Vendors may also email a photo to anlim at stanford.edu. Images should be at least 1024 x 700 (width by height).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>


        <fieldset>
          <legend>Seller's Permit Registration (only for prepaid package)</legend>
        </fieldset>
        <div>
          <p>The prepaid vendor package includes a health permit, but vendors must submit their information to receive a seller’s permit. <strong>This is required for the event, but it is free to register for a seller’s permit.</strong></p> 

          <p><strong>Please follow these steps</strong> to complete your registration. Thank you!</p>

          <ul>
          <li>Go to <%= link_to 'https://efile.boe.ca.gov/ereg/index.boe', 'https://efile.boe.ca.gov/ereg/index.boe' %> and fill out the form.</li>
          <li>Use the following address for the temporary special event:</br>
            <i>519 Lasuen Mall</br>
            Stanford University</br>
            Stanford, CA 94305</i>
          </li>
          <li>Email your completed form to vxiao at stanford.edu.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <fieldset>
          <legend>Terms and Conditions</legend>
        </fieldset>
        <div class="form-group row">
          <div class="offset-sm-2 col-sm-10">
            <div class="form-check">
              <div class="form-check-label">
                <%= f.check_box :agreement, checked: false, id: "inputAgreement", class: 'form-check-input' %>By checking this box, I agree to the terms set above. If selecting the prepaid vendor package, by checking this box, I also confirm that I will register/have registered for a seller’s permit on behalf on my restaurant.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group row">
          <div class="offset-sm-2 col-sm-10">
            <%= submit_tag "Submit", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          </div>
        </div>
       <% end %>
      <p><strong>If you have selected the prepaid package</strong>, you will be contacted soon by Stanford Night Market to confirm your registration.</br>
      <strong>If you have selected the bulk sales package</strong>, you will be contacted soon by a student organization interested in purchasing bulk foods.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>